                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The uncertainty in energy of each measured",
                " data point was estimated from the uncertainty in",
                " incident beam energy, foil thickness and path length",
                " straggling, the latter obtained from a compilation by",
                " Janni."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "DATA-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The total uncertainties in the measured",
                " cross sections and yields were obtained by summing",
                " all the contributing uncertainties in quadrature and",
                " are expressed as standard uncertainties.",
                "The uncertainties due to counting statistics and photo-",
                " peak integration were generally negligible <1%.",
                "In the case of the liquid sources, an additional",
                "  uncertainty of 2% was adopted for the detector",
                "  efficiency, resulting from the experimental",
                "  correction factor for the source geometry.",
                "The systematic uncertainty was estimated to be about",
                " 7%, including the"
              ]
